\f1 Let\'92s take a different approach to the box, smalltext, and box-primary and box-secondary styles. In the last video, for the primary and secondary styles, we included two extend statements in each. This allowed us to keep box as one style, smalltext as a separate style, and primary or secondary as third styles. We could create new styles incorporating elements of just box, or just smalltext.\
